  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p707222/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(128,0,128); line-height: 1.8em;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i1.s.hjfile.cn/entry/201406/c4eb420a-edc1-4d02-9c43-969dc82f4ef1.jpg\" /></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(128,0,128); line-height: 1.8em;\"><strong><a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2566/\" target=\"_blank\">《英闻天天译》</a></strong></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">是一档沪江部落的原创翻译互动节目（</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128,0,128); line-height: 1.8em;\"><a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/15448211001/\"><strong>戳去参与节目&gt;&gt;&gt;</strong></a></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">），主持人提供翻译参考文本，对大家递交的翻译作品进行点评，和大家共同进步！本期节目选取的是关于</span>经济影响文学<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">的</span><span style=\"font-family: verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(51,51,51); line-height: 28px;\">一则英文报道，让我们一起在翻译中关注</span><font color=\"#333333\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">。</font></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><span style=\"border-top: 0px;\"><span style=\"border-top: 0px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\"><img /></span></span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><span style=\"border-top: 0px;\"><span style=\"border-top: 0px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\"><strong>SUMMARY：</strong></span></span></span></p>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span><span>总统在第二个任期内一般会给自己的团队补充些新鲜血液。2006年，乔治&middot;W &middot;布什进行了团队重组，也可以说是这次重组挽救了他的总统任期。巴拉克&middot;奥巴马现在正面临一个类似的时期，并且有迹象表明，他希望在11月国会选举之后做一些人事变动。</span></span></div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">CONTENT：</strong></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPresidents value loyalty, to be sure, and Obama must be feeling especially grateful for team players after publication this week of Leon Panetta&rsquo;s scorching memoir. It&rsquo;s a bitter irony that after assembling his famous &ldquo;team of rivals&rdquo; &mdash; strong, independent personalities such as Panetta, Robert Gates and Hillary Clinton &mdash; Obama found himself <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/second-guess\" target=\"_blank\">second-guess</a>ed in memoirs by the former secretaries of defense and state. The next president may decide to include a nondisclosure form along with the oath of office for Cabinet hires.<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tObama&rsquo;s current team can&rsquo;t be faulted for disloyalty. And if they all stay on board for the last two years, that would at least delay publication of their <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/autobiography\" target=\"_blank\">autobiographies</a>. But loyalty aside, Obama appears to be interested in a talent infusion that would add depth and expertise; a model was his recent appointment of retired Gen. John Allen as special <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/envoy\" target=\"_blank\">envoy</a> for Iraq and Syria. More such top-level hires may be coming in an effort to widen the administration&rsquo;s bandwidth.</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0,100,0);\"><strong>【沪江英语小编】</strong></span>大家在查看主持人提供的翻译版本前，可以先自己进行尝试翻译练习，只有在不断的翻译中翻译能力才能有所提升哦！<br />\n\t轻松注册沪江，马上参与<strong><a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2566/\">【英闻天天译】</a></strong>节目练翻译&rarr;<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2566/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/810ca373cf4442a188b39dd8ff64425f.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>本期节目参考译文：</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(128,128,128);\">（参考译文由该节目主持人提供，仅供参考，欢迎大家讨论）</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><strong>参考译文1：</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"replyview red\">\n\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\">总统们都看重忠诚，这是肯定的，而在本周莱昂&middot;帕内塔尖酸刻薄的回忆录出版后，奥巴马真应该特别感谢他的团队成员。更具讽刺意味的是，他的团队包含了帕内塔、罗伯特&middot;盖茨、希拉里&middot;克林顿这样坚强、独立的竞争对手，这一著名的&ldquo;竞争对手团队&rdquo;组成之后，奥巴马发现自己在前国务卿的回忆录中早就被言中了。这第二个任期中的内阁成员可能会以保密的形式宣誓入职。<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t奥巴马目前的团队不能被职责为不忠。但如果他们在过去两年中是同舟共济的，那至少会推迟出版自传。但是除了忠诚，奥巴马似乎更有意通过引进人才，增加团队的深度和专业度；一个例子是他最近任命了退休将军约翰&middot;艾伦为伊拉克和叙利亚特使。更多这样顶级的成员加入可能会为政府拓宽统一战线。</span></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><span style=\"color: #000;\"><strong>参考译文2：</strong></span></span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"replyview red\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><span style=\"color: #000;\">毫无疑问总统们总是会把忠诚度看的很重。想来本周里昂&middot;帕内塔激情澎湃的回忆录出版之后，奥巴马总统会尤为感激自己的团队。这确实是个辛辣的讽刺，特别是在他组建了著名的有着性格强硬独立的帕内塔、盖茨和希拉里的&ldquo;政敌团队&rdquo;后。奥巴马发现在这些前国务卿、国防部长写的回忆录中，自己已经被看透了。下任总统也许会考虑在内阁成员宣誓就职时增加一条保密条款。<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t奥巴马的现有团队不应该因为不忠而受到指责。如果在过去两年内他们都呆在美国以外，那么至少他们的自传出版时间会被推迟。但是放着忠诚不谈，奥巴马开始表现出对于人才输入的兴趣，这将拓宽人才渠道提升人才专业性。最近的一个例子是他任命了约翰艾伦将军为伊拉克叙利亚外交特别使节。为了努力拓宽政府带宽，这类高级别雇佣应当会在接下来大量增加。</span></span></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t想要得到主持人专业的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/15448211001/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255,0,0);\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</span></a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p707222/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p707222\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul styl