  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); padding: 0px; line-height: 25px; font-family: verdana, arial; margin: 1em 0px;\">\n\t<strong>背景：</strong></p>\n<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); padding: 0px; line-height: 25px; font-family: verdana, arial; margin: 1em 0px;\">\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); padding: 0px; line-height: 25px; font-family: verdana, arial; margin: 1em 0px;\">\n\tCanada is, without a doubt, a country of immigrants. The first groups of people, in the 1800's, were citizens of France and England hoping to create a better life in the New World. Not much has changed, other than now we have citizens who originated from all over Europe, Asia, the Americas, Australia, and Africa. They, though, did not just <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/originate\" target=\"_blank\">originate</a> there; they brought a piece of their home to their new country.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tFor Sunday topic, please select one listed below to share your thoughts:<br />\n\t1. What do you think of Canada's cultural <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/mosaic\" target=\"_blank\">mosaic</a>?<br />\n\t2. What circumstance could form the cultural mosaic or like melting pot?<br />\n\t3. Open discussion: Canadian Diversity (You can do some research and share your ideas)</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tCanada is a country which embraces diverse cultures, not like a mixing pot to blend everyone into a single and conformed identity. It also prides itself worldwide as a country made up of a cultural mosaic rather than a cultural melting pot. The mosaic is based on their belief that Canada as a whole becomes stronger by having immigrants bring with their cultural diversity for all Canadians to learn from. The cultural melting pot, as adopted in the United States, tells immigrants that no matter who they have been in the past, upon landing on American shores, they are Americans and are expected to adopt and the follow the American way. In my opinion, cultural mosaic is a very harmonious way of combination while respects and keeps the uniqueness of different cultures.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/item/913586/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p706532/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p706532\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p706698/\">看懂《星际穿越》 必须了解的物理知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p706702/\">发型很重要：“暮光”男主奇葩新发型</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p706765/\">“Fuck”的正确使用方法  图文并茂！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p615096/\">电影咖必学：与电影密切相关的英语词汇</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p707364/\">Vape 牛津词典评出2014年度热词</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p707342/\">全球幸福指数排名 越南第二中国60</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p707179/\">是爱还是喜欢？小测试说出你的心（答案）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p707312/\">别人家的护照 挪威极光护照美如画</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p707307/\">不男不女 波兰奇葩理由封杀小熊维尼</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
